	width=&#34;3472&#34;
	height=&#34;4640&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://oddyti.com/post/wuchao/%E8%8D%89%E8%8E%93%E7%86%8A_hu8034877273163433347.jpg 480w, https://oddyti.com/post/wuchao/%E8%8D%89%E8%8E%93%E7%86%8A_hu3321775496268389705.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;草莓熊&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;74&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;179px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;深山里竟然也有麦麦（麦门永存！）&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://oddyti.com/post/wuchao/%E9%BA%A6%E9%97%A8.jpg&#34;
